@@ -0,0 +1,26 @@
+# Hermes OS Update Safety Gate
+
+This backup repository is part of the Hermes OS core-update safety process.
+Before any Hermes Agent core update reaches the live runtime, the backup must be
+fresh enough to restore the protected Hermes OS control-plane files.
+
+## Required pre-update checks
+
+1. Clone this repository with `--depth 1`.
+2. Verify `restore/MANIFEST.json` exists.
+3. Verify all paths in `restore/PROTECTED_FILES.yaml` exist.
+4. From the live Hermes Agent checkout, run:
+
+   ```bash
+   python3 tools/hermes_backup_freshness_gate.py --pretty
+   ```
+
+5. If the report says `blocking: true`, refresh this backup before updating core.
+6. Only proceed with core update after local dev, live runtime, launcher parity,
+   policy validator, and gateway/Telegram smoke checks pass.
+
+## Restore warning
+
+Do not use this repository as a blind filesystem overlay. Restore selected files
+according to `restore/PROTECTED_FILES.yaml` and re-run policy/launcher/gateway
+smoke tests before claiming success.
